        <h3><span class="icon-medium icon-transportation-yellow"></span>Transportation is included</h3>
        <p>Tropical Ruby will provide nice and confortable buses to all attendees at the days of conference (<strong>March 6th &amp; 7th</strong>). It’ll depart at early morning and trips directly to the event. The journey back will be after the conference, at night. <a href="/en/schedule/march-5">See more</a>.</p>
