        <h3><span class="icon-medium icon-bed-yellow"></span>Where to spend the nights</h3>
        <p>There are a lot of lodging options in Recife and Porto de Galinhas, from luxurious resorts to simple bed &amp; breakfast hotels. If you need help about accomodations, please send an e-mail to the conference official travel agency: <a href="mailto:eventos@pontestur.com.br" target="_blank">eventos@pontestur.com.br</a></p>
