      </div>
      <div class="remark-item">
        <h3><span class="icon-medium icon-beachball"></span>Prepare for a sunny weather</h3>
        <p>It is always hot in this region of Brazil, so expect a warm weather with temperatures between 72 ºF and 86 ºF (22 ºC and 30ºC), high humidity and occasional rain. Remember to bring sunscreen and protective accessories such as sunglasses and hat.</p>
